                                  int currentIteration,

                                  double toleranz)
        prints how many iterations the program executed and which break condition was triggered and compares the conditions with final result.
        Parameters:
        iterationCondition - true when the maximum iterations equal the current iteration
        qualityCondition - true when the final deviation is smaller than the custom deviation
        currentIteration - how many iterations the program executed
        maxIterations - iteration break condition
        deviation - final deviation
        toleranz - deviation break condition
